         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Shire of Ballaarat ¶ Shire Office. ¶ Learmonth ¶  12. 4.  ¶ 18 ¶ 86. ¶ To The Right Honourable Baron Von Müller, C.M.G., M. &amp; Ph.D., F.R.S., ¶ Melbourne....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">86.04.12</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Henry Bregenzer</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M197, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">MS annotation</seg>: 'Answ 16/4/86 F.v.M'; letter not found. <seg style="">MS annotation by J. H. Willis</seg>: 'Centaurea calcitrapa'.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Shire of Ballaarat</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Shire Office.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Learmonth</seg> 12. 4. <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">18</seg>86.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">To The Right Honourable Baron Von Müller, C.M.G., M. &amp; Ph.D., F.R.S.,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My Lord,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honour to request that you will favor me by stating the name of the enclosed plant, botanical and common, it being a sample of a large amount found growing on some roads (frequently traversed by travelling sheep) within the Shire of Ballarat.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In my opinion the seed has been conveyed into the shire by above mentioned sheep.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It grows into a bush about 18 inches in hight and diameter, blumes in March and April, ripenes in Spring, becoming quite dry and forming into a spherical shape, and in Summer blows along the roads, spreading its seeds.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honour to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My Lord,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your Lordship's most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Henry Bregenzer</p>
         </div>
